pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: Deta yomwe ikuwonetsedwa pa dashboard iyi imasonkhanitsidwa mwachindunji kuchokera ku mayankho a kafukufuku ndipo sichichokera ku ziwerengero za dziko lovomerezeka kapena deta. Zimaimira malingaliro omwe achinyamata adafotokoza panthawi ya kafukufukuyu, ndipo mfundo iliyonse yomwe yatengedwa kuchokera ku mayankho awa ndi udindo wa wogwiritsa ntchito, osati PMNCH. PMNCH yadzipereka kulemekeza, kulimbikitsa ndi kuteteza ufulu ndi ubwino wa anthu onse. Malingaliro aliwonse omwe akufotokozedwa mu mayankho a kafukufuku kapena zipangizo zofalitsidwa zomwe zikutuluka pa dashboard iyi zomwe zimatsutsana ndi kudzipereka kumeneku sizikuvomerezedwa ndi PMNCH.
